          h4.h4 Learn about the Habitat Operator for Kubernetes
          h6.h6 GITHUB
          p
            | The Habitat Operator is a Kubernetes controller designed to solve running and auto-managing Habitat Services on Kubernetes. It does this by making use of Custom Resource Definitions.&nbsp;
            | Explore the Habitat Operator project on GitHub.
      div.columns.small-12.large-6.np-right
